casebody.data:
Janet YIJUAN FOU, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Joe ZHUOWU FOU, Defendant. (Kevin Tung - Petitioner) C-972 September Term 2018
082245 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001569-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs; and it is further.

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
